com.misc.common.moplaf.solver

Interface GeneratorGoal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GeneratorElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GeneratorLpGoal
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneratorGoalImpl, GeneratorLpGoalImpl

    public interface GeneratorGoal
extends GeneratorElement
    A representation of the model object 'Generator Goal'. A goal for the generated problem. A goal is expected to be directly contained to its Generator owner. A goal may reference a secondary goal: a subgoal.

    The following features are supported:

    • Generator
    • Name
    • Selected Solution Display
    • Label
    • Solution
    • Objective Type
    See Also:
    SolverPackage.getGeneratorGoal()
